column5: My place is close the DFW and Love airports, restaurants, & Baylor Scott & White Medical Center. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers. Large Kitchen, shared clean bathroom, lock on bedroom door, clean towels & linens, high quality queen size bed, and hardwood floors. Cable television with over 150 HD channels is in the room.
